T02D2320:263b-1: ko ti nishtha pha la pra d'i pa n'a ma /
T02D2320:263b-3: mthar thug 'bras bu'i sgron ma zhes bya ba /
T02D2320:263b-4: 'jam dpal smra ba'i seng ge la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2320:263b-5: 'khor ba'i chu las sgrol mdzad pa //
T02D2320:263b-6: dam pa skyes mchog rnams la 'dud //
T02D2320:263b-7: sgrub pa'i chos la don yod pas //
T02D2320:263b-8: dam pas gsungs la yid ches kyis //
T02D2320:263b-9: mthar thug 'bras bu'i sgron ma ni //
T02D2320:263b-10: rnam pa gnyis su shes par bya //
T02D2320:263b-11: gnas skabs rgyu yi 'bras bu dang //
T02D2320:263b-13: rgyu mthun 'bras bu rab ster bas //
T02D2320:263b-14: byas pa'i chos la nan tan skyed //
T02D2320:263b-15: nam mkha' rdo rje grong 'jug gsum //
T02D2320:263b-16: las su rung ba'i 'bras bu yin //
T02D2320:263b-17: rtogs pa'i 'bras bu sku lnga ste //
T02D2320:263b-18: ngo bo stong pa chos skul //
T02D2320:263b-19: rang bzhin gsal ba longs sku yin //
T02D2320:263b-20: mtshan nyid nyams myong sprul pa'i sku //
T02D2320:263b-21: zung 'jug ngo bo nyid kyi sku //
T02D2320:263b-22: rang grol rang dag bde chen sku //
T02D2320:263b-23: don la mtshon du ci yang med //
T02D2320:263b-24: tha snyad blo la rgyu 'bras d'i pam gnyis //
T02D2320:263b-25: zhen pa bzlog phyir bstan pa las //
T02D2320:263b-26: don dam brjod du med pas na //
T02D2320:263b-27: rgyal bas tshig gcig gsungs pa med //
